<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f9;
            color: #2d3436;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            width: 90%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #2d3436;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .success-icon {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #e3f9e5;
            color: #2b8a3e;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
            background-color: #4b6bfb;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(75, 107, 251, 0.15);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #3557fa;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(75, 107, 251, 0.25);
        }
        .plex-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
            background-color: #ffb142;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 177, 66, 0.15);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .plex-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff9f1a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 177, 66, 0.25);
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #4b6bfb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            body {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 2rem;
                width: 85%;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .button-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
        <h1>Subscription Successful!</h1>
        <p>Thank you, {{ .UserInfo.Username }}! Your subscription will be activated soon.</p>
        <p>An invite will be sent to your Plex account shortly.</p>
        <p>You may need to accept the invite within your Plex account to gain full access.</p>
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/" class="button home-button">Return Home</a>
            <a href="https://app.plex.tv/desktop/#!/settings/manage-library-access" class="plex-button">Check Plex Requests</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
